content:
Guest Access to D2C Stores Is Automatically Enabled

You no longer need to manually turn on guest access when a D2C store is created. Your guests can browse, make purchases, and get a hassle-free shopping experience the moment that your store is active. After guest access is enabled automatically, the Guest User profile is created, sharing settings are turned on, and person accounts is mapped as the default record type.

Where: This change applies to D2C Commerce in Enterprise, Unlimited, and Developer editions.
title: Guest Access Automatically Enabled in D2C Stores
